<h3 class="heading orange"><b>Careers at Traix</b></h3>
<p>Our focus on growing that drives us to step out of our ease zone and scale new altitudes every day. We are on a mission to disrupt habits and pause existing mind-sets. Constant innovation makes this a veracity. With our diverse workforce, lateral thinking and creativity, our work is a reflection of our thinking.</p>
<p>If you think you are motivated enough to deal with challenging problems, shifting the status quo and doing your bit to shape the world around you give us a shout.</p>
<%#<p id="notice"><%= notice </p>%>

<h4 class="heading"><b>Current Openings</b></h4>

<% @careers.each do |career| %>
  <% if career.status=='Open' %>
    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-3" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
      <div class=" progbox">
        <b><%= link_to career.position, career_path(career.id), :alt=>career.position %></b>
      </div>
    </div>
  <%end%>
<%end%>
<br>
<% if trainer_signed_in? %>
  <% if current_trainer.role =='admin' %>
    <h4 class="heading"><b>Closed Jobs</b></h4>
    <% @careers.each do |career| %>
      <% if career.status=='Closed' %>
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-3" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
          <div class=" progbox">
            <b><%= link_to career.position, career_path(career.id), :alt=>career.position %></b>
          </div>
        </div>
      <%end%>
    <%end%>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
      <%= link_to 'Add Openings', new_career_path, :class=>"btn btn-success" %>
    </div>
  <%end%>
<%end%>